# Set default behavior to normalize all text files to LF line endings in the repository.
# On checkout, files will be converted to the native line ending (CRLF on Windows).
* text=auto eol=lf

# Explicitly declare common text files for your project.
*.py text
*.js text
*.jsx text
*.html text
*.css text
*.md text
*.json text
.gitignore text
.env text

# Mark specific file types as binary so Git doesn't try to change their line endings.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary